================================================================================
Conclusion
================================================================================

SHA-256 implementation successfully demonstrates:
- Cryptographic hash function properties (one-way, avalanche, fixed output)
- Application to file integrity verification
- Application to password storage (with and without salt)
- Importance of salt in preventing rainbow table attacks

For production systems, use specialized password hashing algorithms
(bcrypt, scrypt, Argon2id) rather than SHA-256 alone.

